## Component Philosophy
- Dashboard is the hero experience — behavioral risk front and center
- Every insight must be data-backed and cite specific numbers
- Never shame users for spending — provide awareness and agency
- Spine is not a budgeting app — do not build budget-setting features in v1
- The "aha moment" is: "I spent $X extra because of poor sleep" — make that number visible
